headline: Is It Time to Reassess Northrop Grumman After Stealth Fighter Contract Headlines?
summary: Trying to figure out what to do with Northrop Grumman stock? You are definitely not alone. With defense headlines frequently appearing and Northrop Grumman’s recent surge, it is easy to see why investors are giving this defense giant a second look. After all, the stock has gained an impressive 32.2% year-to-date, and is up a solid 7.5% over the past month. That is not just noise in a choppy market, and it does not hurt that the five-year return stands at 116.0%, a figure many stocks can only...
